Easy Creamy Cajun Shrimp Fettuccine Ingredients ⬇️

- Half Onion Diced
- 1 Bell Pepper Diced
- 1 cup cheddar cheese
- 1 cup Parmesan 
- Half block cream cheese *cubed*

- 1/2 teaspoon flour 
- 1 Pound Cooked Fettuccine Noodles
